---
/**
 * CheatModal.astro
 * 開發者作弊模態框 - 通過連續點擊 5 次頭像觸發
 */
---

<div class="cheat-modal" id="cheat-modal">
  <div class="cheat-modal-content">
    <div class="cheat-header">
      <h3><i class="fas fa-gamepad"></i> 開發者模式</h3>
      <button class="cheat-close" id="cheat-close"><i class="fas fa-times"></i></button>
    </div>
    <div class="cheat-body">
      <div class="cheat-section">
        <h4><i class="fas fa-skull"></i> 平行世界重置</h4>
        <p>殺死這個平行世界的蓋倫，獲得全新的開始</p>
        <button class="cheat-button danger" id="reset-world">重置世界</button>
      </div>

      <div class="cheat-section">
        <h4><i class="fas fa-coins"></i> 金幣作弊</h4>
        <p>輸入數字增加金幣數量</p>
        <div class="cheat-input-group">
          <input type="number" id="gold-input" placeholder="輸入金幣數量" min="0">
          <button class="cheat-button primary" id="add-gold">增加金幣</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cheat-section">
        <h4><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> 狀態回滿</h4>
        <p>瞬間恢復蓋倫的所有狀態值</p>
        <button class="cheat-button success" id="restore-status">回滿狀態</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- 樣式由全局 _cheat.scss 提供 -->
